headline: Environmental and Facilities Services Stocks Q2 Results: Benchmarking Veralto (NYSE:VLTO)
summary: Quarterly earnings results are a good time to check in on a company’s progress, especially compared to its peers in the same sector. Today we are looking at Veralto (NYSE:VLTO) and the best and worst performers in the environmental and facilities services industry.
